e20ff612fe93d35251f37e702bc5b572ea9a413a980c42228a26f411e408858dffadd4340a04e32430753b83ce618a546cf4abe6835727fbb7fa9bf1c4375bc4  0001-Add-provisioner-for-Alpine-Linux.patch
"
